Masters officially complete. Feels so good to close this loop ➰ 6 years in the making. Thank you to my alma mater @westerniluniv for never giving up on me! Look out world…
I love these bunzingas to the cosmos and back, and back again. 💫💖 happy new year everyone. May 2023 bring you love, healing, joy, magic and miracles. And so it is.

l am taking a year long program (for a second time) hosted by my teacher turned friend Katie at @theshaktischool. This is a course on Ayurvedic Wellness - which covers everything from functional medicine, psychology, neuroscience, holistic healing and women’s wisdom. Last year this time I started my studies in Ayurveda and it’s been a deep portal of discovery for me - from the food I eat, to the connection I have to my body and creator, to my ability to tune into my inner guidance. So here I am - back again for another 12 months to go even deeper on this ride. 🧘‍♀️✨🌎🌱🙏

Happiness: a clear horizon with nothing to worry about on your plate. Not ranks, trophies, possessions or bank accounts. I’ve learned recently that I can find this feeling in the subtleties. Noticing what I haven’t and being tuned into to the magic. Birds chirping.. dogs playing… the ac running.. wind whistling. It’s all the music of life 🎶🕊️🫶

Every year TR hosts a free seminar for the WORLD. Like anyone can come, for free, for 5 days. This pic is from when the tradition started four challenges ago… so much has changed 🤪 It’s been such a blessing to support this work and it’s extension to all of you. I feel there’s something bigger at play and that feels deeply meaningful. Anywho, the challenge is back, it’s only day 2 so plenty of time to join in and start making your life a masterpiece. No better time than the present to get honest, assess what’s real, listen to what your soul is craving and take some big bold beautiful action. 💖💫 www.becomeunshakeable.com will get you in. Come join!!

Such a blast and honor supporting my mentor @tonyrobbins and over a million incredible humans this past week at the Unshakeable challenge. Here’s to the big beautiful amazing lives we’re all creating… 💫🥳💖🍭😎🙌 may the blessings be abundant!

Swipe for the coolest most epic team on the planet. Although many are not pictured. It takes a village. 🙏
Family business 🫶

A total privilege and honor today celebrating the 50th anniversary of Title IX and National Girls and Women in Sport Day at my alma mater. We are so lucky that courageous souls paved the path for us to play today… it did not happen without sacrifice and 50 years really was not that long ago. Maya Angelou says humility is acknowledging there are people before me who found the path, and for that I am so so grateful. To all the female athletes out there - let’s honor those that went first by always remembering and acknowledging their history. Or… HERstory🙏🙌

social_posts.post_text: Tend to the soul everyday 🕊️
Weekend chronicles 🌸🌻💕

Unconditional trust. No motive. Just open to the lessons. Willing to sit with and explore them all. A full embrace of life’s symphonic range. 🦋🙏🫶🙌 🎷these clips span back 3 years. I’ve loved this wild journey so much, every flavor of it. I’ve learned life is always trying to communicate to us and when we tune in we hear. Or see. Or know.. either of those will do. But trust is the secret ingredient… at least in my own experience.🌻

Banger year let me tell ya 😛

Seriously I chose to get these in maybe 12 seconds. I got the ping. Trusted my gut. And feel like I’ve always been meant to have them. With each passing year I continue to remember who I am. And that feels so good. 🦋

Life has been swirly, funny and miraculous lately. Everyday I’m offered an opportunity to allow life to guide me. To release my grip on how I want it to be. To fall in love with the subtle magic all around. Grateful to be on the journey with you all. More magic this year! Gotta believe it to see it 🪄

Closing out a chapter in my life and have been reflecting a lot lately ~ on the gifts, the lessons and how it needed to happen exactly as it did to show me and teach me what I was ready and meant to learn. Seeing this as a completion I’ve found is so much more empowering than an “end”. I feel complete with the chapter I am transcending. I am grateful for the teachings, the lessons and the space it’s held for me to blossom in many new ways 🌸 completions are a beautiful time ~ for they come with lightness. It’s a letting go, a detaching, a cleaning up… and on the other side is a bit more free version of us with space to welcome the new. 🙏🦋 And so it is… 

Also how long is too long to sit on the @biomatofficial a day? Praying the limit does not exist 🤣🙏

Good morning 🌞💛 I’ve been adjusting my sleep to sync up with mama nature. Partly from my studies in Ayurveda and also because it feels so natural to wake and wind down with the sun and star gaze at night. We have these insane shows 🌟🌝🌅 everyday available for us to be in awe of! So lucky we are… so so lucky.

Happy leap year birthday to the boss man extraordinaire @tonyrobbins 🥳 !!!!!! A one in a million human and I’m grateful to learn from you in this timeline. How it all happened I have no idea but I’m sure glad it did. 🙏🙏🙏 thank you for everything. (Yes I’m standing on a stool!)

When did you stop seeing the world this way? For me it was when I was little. I’m so deeply grateful for my true sight coming back alive. Seeing creation’s stunning magic in the simple and ordinary moments is whats been my source of joy this year. Touching a flower, watching dew fall down a blade of grass, the reflection of the sky in my dogs eyes, the buzz of possibility in the morning, the glamor of the night sky… endless ways to feel blown away by existence. Pretty freaking cool. ❤️

My first little beach house ~ this is what my creative process can look like! I’m deep in a birthing process in this video which means lots of stillness, thinking, breathing, feeling into what is coming through then BOOM flow it out into the keyboard. My dream life is writing everyday in a beautiful environment. I recently bought a new home and am excited to allow my personality to be expressed in the decor. Taking it slowwww and allowing it to come together piece by piece. We’re in our feminine era of creation, healing, and EXPRESSION. May any shred of untruth fall away so the realest parts of me can come alive. And so it is!!

Been DEEP in it y’all! Life has been teaching me and inviting me to step forward into a deeper aspect of myself ~ one that I’ve been getting to know these last few months. I am really proud of myself for the faithful path I’ve chosen to walk. I’m so grateful. I trust more than ever. I surrender to the guidance. I accept what is. And I give thanks for it all. 🙏🤲

A little over a month ago I had the opportunity to host a very special event for @officiallymcconaughey ~ and I wouldn’t have been considered for that if I didn’t have the worlds best mentors to teach me on my journey. Many of them pictured in these slides!

Reflecting today. A year ago sweet Nellie joined my little family and it’s wild just how much has transformed since that day, including myself. Me a year ago genuinely registers as a different person. I love how in hindsight we can connect dots and see what the Universe had up its sleeve, hidden in all the plot twists, surprises and experiences ~ both light and dark. I have absolutely no flocking clue what the future will look like which makes the possibilities endless, delicious and full of adventure 😻 I’m not trying to outsmart the U anymore ~ no 3 year, 5 year goals, etc. I have north stars and moonshots… but I MUCH prefer to feel into my desires and be absolutely STUNNED, shocked, surprised, floored and baffled how they come to fruition. Here for it all. Happy Sunday 🙏

I love you!!!!

Lost in the sauce of life and forgot my anni!!! A lot has changed in five years. I’m older, wiser, more grounded & open, a deeper listener, a better lover and friend, and overall a more connected, happy, and present version of me. I owe it all to the fateful day I found my way to Tony’s work 7 years ago (through literally a flyer in a familiar Chicago elevator). There aren’t words to match my depth of gratitude… 🙏 I’ve marched through the sludge of my edges and ultimately put my student hat on to learn 📚. This wild ride is a mystery and I’m sooo grateful to experience the full range of it all. Grateful in advance for all I have yet to learn. All the growth. Thank you my mentor @tonyrobbins for making this path possible. Excited to meet the next evolution of me in another 5!💗

What happens when there is truly nothing to gain?

What happens when you stop trying to have a special experience?

Darkness retreat initiates us into a completely unadorned meeting with ourselves.

Suspended in space - with nothing to hold to - raw - open - vulnerable - safe 

What remains?

What remains when we stop prioritizing everything that comes and goes?

What remains when we stop romanticizing our lives?

What remains when we’re tenderly honest with what matters most?

“Stop trying to heal yourself, fix yourself, even awaken yourself. Instead, bow deeply to yourself as you actually are.” ~ Jeff Foster
